flowchart TB
    Start([Customer sends Hi]):::entry --> CheckDB{Mobile in DB?}:::decision
    CheckDB -->|New| NewCust[Collect Name, Address,<br/>Google Map, Landmark]:::customer
    NewCust --> SaveCust[(Save customer)]:::db
    SaveCust --> Menu
    CheckDB -->|Existing| Menu{{Main Menu}}:::customer

    Menu --> M1[Price List]:::customer
    Menu --> M2[Place Order]:::customer
    Menu --> M3[Check Order]:::customer
    Menu --> M4[Update Address]:::customer
    Menu --> M5[Contact Support]:::customer

    M1 --> Catalog[Show catalog<br/>admin-editable<br/>Min 5 - Free pickup & delivery]:::catalog
    Catalog --> Menu

    M4 --> NewCust

    M5 --> Support[Help options:<br/>Missing / Damage / Delay /<br/>Payment / Other]:::support
    Support --> Ticket[(Create ticket<br/>notify admin)]:::db

    M3 --> ViewOrders[List active orders<br/>multiple allowed]:::customer
    ViewOrders --> CancelChk{Before Collected?}:::decision
    CancelChk -->|Yes| CanCancel[Cancel Order button]:::customer
    CancelChk -->|No| NoCancel[No cancel -<br/>Contact Support]:::error

    M2 --> Qty[Ask quantity]:::customer
    Qty --> MinChk{Qty >= 5?}:::decision
    MinChk -->|No| RejectMin[Minimum is 5 -<br/>add more items]:::error
    RejectMin --> Qty
    MinChk -->|Yes| Date[Pickup date:<br/>Today / Tomorrow]:::customer
    Date --> Time[Pickup time:<br/>Morning / Afternoon / Evening]:::customer
    Time --> ConfirmQ{Confirm?}:::decision
    ConfirmQ -->|No| Menu
    ConfirmQ -->|Yes| Placed[Order placed - #ID]:::status

    Placed --> AdminCard[(Admin order card<br/>+ instant alert)]:::admin
    AdminCard --> Assign[Admin assigns partner<br/>from dropdown]:::admin
    Assign --> Link[Send signed token link<br/>scoped to partner + today<br/>expires 11:59 PM]:::partner
    Link --> Dash[Partner dashboard<br/>Call / Navigate / Reached /<br/>Picked / Cant Make It]:::partner

    Dash --> AvailQ{Cant Make It?}:::decision
    AvailQ -->|Yes| Unassign[Order -> Unassigned<br/>highlighted for admin]:::error
    Unassign --> Assign
    AvailQ -->|No| Picked[Picked - take photo<br/>tick any issues]:::partner

    Picked --> DmgQ{Issues found?}:::decision
    DmgQ -->|No| S1
    DmgQ -->|Yes| AskCust[Send photo + issues<br/>Do you accept?]:::customer
    AskCust --> RespQ{Customer response}:::decision
    RespQ -->|Yes| S1
    RespQ -->|Call Us| Support
    RespQ -->|No reply 1-2h| Auto[Auto-accept<br/>notify customer]:::status
    Auto --> S1

    S1[Collected]:::status --> S2[Reached Shop]:::status
    S2 --> S3[Ironing Started]:::status
    S3 --> S4[Ready]:::status
    S4 --> PayQ{Payment mode}:::decision
    PayQ -->|Cash| S5
    PayQ -->|Razorpay| PayLink[Send invoice + link<br/>final price locked]:::payment
    PayLink --> S5[Out for Delivery]:::status
    S5 --> S6[Delivered]:::status

    Invalid[Invalid input fallback:<br/>Please use the buttons below]:::error -.applies at every step.-> Menu

    classDef entry fill:#0EA5E9,stroke:#0369A1,color:#fff
    classDef customer fill:#10B981,stroke:#047857,color:#fff
    classDef decision fill:#F59E0B,stroke:#B45309,color:#1f2937
    classDef admin fill:#6366F1,stroke:#3730A3,color:#fff
    classDef partner fill:#EC4899,stroke:#9D174D,color:#fff
    classDef status fill:#14B8A6,stroke:#0F766E,color:#fff
    classDef payment fill:#84CC16,stroke:#4D7C0F,color:#1f2937
    classDef error fill:#EF4444,stroke:#991B1B,color:#fff
    classDef support fill:#A855F7,stroke:#6B21A8,color:#fff
    classDef catalog fill:#F97316,stroke:#9A3412,color:#fff
    classDef db fill:#475569,stroke:#1e293b,color:#fff
